bilingual.source: The decoration on the first float in the parade was spectacular.
bilingual.target: 游行中第一个花车上的装饰很壮观。

bilingual.source: On that day they will go shopping together and watch the parade.
bilingual.target: 那天他们会一起去购物并观看游行。

bilingual.source: It featured a parade and a great feast with music, dancing, and sports.
bilingual.target: 它以游行和盛大的音乐、舞蹈和体育盛宴为特色。

bilingual.source: The female soldiers forming the biggest group in the National Day parade attracted a lot of interest from the media.
bilingual.target: 在国庆游行中，组成最大方阵的女兵引起了媒体的极大兴趣。
在胜利日，我们会举行游行。
这个游行每年都会举行。

bilingual.source: There is a big parade on May 1st.
bilingual.target: 五月一号有一个大型游行。

bilingual.source: There are many floats in the parade.
bilingual.target: 游行队伍里有很多花车。

bilingual.source: The crowd hoor as the parade passes by.

list.abstract: Parade（英[pəˈreɪd]，美[pəˈreɪd]），英语单词，作名词为游行；公共广场；散步广场。作动词为游行；列队行进；招摇而行。短语搭配有identification parade（嫌犯集体示众）。例句为“Officers will parade through the town centre.（军官们将列队经过市中心。）” Parade名词类近义词有display、pageant等，动词类show off、brag about。procession是指举行庆祝活动或盛大仪式时庄严行进的有秩序的游行队伍或行列。
《Parade》是由布雷西亚组合Vinai制作的一首舞曲，单曲于2017年12月18日通过华纳唱片公司发行。

yingyinNormal.en: What do you watch on thanksgiving? The parade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你们感恩节看什么？游行。

yingyinNormal.en: My Hong Kong parade preparation has started much earlier.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的香港游行准备工作更早就开始啦。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a tradition, like the parade. If the parade decided it was gay, moved out, and abandoned its entire family.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这跟游行一样，是一项传统，如果游行也包括同性恋和抛妻弃子的话。

yingyinNormal.en: And every other Saturday, he had to march in a parade and wave flowers at tyrants.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每两周的周六他都得参加游行，为一位暴君欢呼。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the start of the famous night parade which will be kicking off in just a couple of hours.
yingyinNormal.zh: 著名的夜间大游行即将在几个小时之后开始。

yingyinNormal.en: Lily, your daddy may have missed the parade, but he was all over Halloween.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莉莉，你大爸或许错过了游行，但他真是为万圣节用尽了心思。

yingyinNormal.en: A huge audience the parade draws attracts performers from all over the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 来看游行的观众非常之多，这也吸引了来自世界各地的表演者。

yingyinNormal.en: Come on, get ready. It's almost time for the Halloween parade. You're supposed to knock!
yingyinNormal.zh: 来吧，准备好。万圣节游行要开始了。你应该敲门的！

yingyinNormal.en: Leonard stood on me once, too, but he was just trying to see the Rose Parade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱纳德也曾经站在我背上过，他当时是为了站高点看新年玫瑰花车大游行。

yingyinNormal.en: They think it's going to be the biggest parade ever, with 150,000 people or more lining the streets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 预计起码有15万人排列街边，这将会是史上最盛大的游行。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. After all we weigh it down, we could walk it right over there. Like a parade balloon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，毕竟我们把它拉下来了，我们可以从那儿走过去，就像游行气球一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Step 6: Attend a Chinese New Year parade, one of the most popular ways to celebrate the holiday's hopeful spirit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第六步：参加中国新年游行，这是最受欢迎的方式之一来庆祝新年新气象。

yingyinNormal.en: You think you deserve a reward for being a good person, that we should celebrate your goodness. Would you like a parade?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你认为表现好应该得到奖励，我们应该庆祝你好的表现。你想要个游行吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, technically, each of us comes with a lunch in a basket but let's not kid ourselves. This was a beefcake parade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然我们每个人都在篮子里放了午饭，但还是不要自欺欺人了，这是裸男大游行。

yingyinNormal.en: And when he got food poisoning at the Rose Bowl Parade, he begged a deity he doesn't believe in to end his life quickly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他在玫瑰碗橄榄球赛游行时食物中毒，还求过一个他不信奉的神让他死得痛快。

yingyinNormal.en: I expected to see Howard throw the baseball, finish my hot dog, and hightail it across the street to Disneyland just in time for Mickey's Soundsational Parade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我以为看霍华德投球，吃完热狗，麻利地过街去迪士尼乐园，正好赶上米奇的音乐大游行。

yingyinNormal.en: That's right. To protect you. Tell me, Bernard. If you were to proclaim your humanity to the world, what do you imagine would greet you? A ticker-tape parade, perhaps?
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，为了保护你，告诉我，伯纳德，如果你要对世界昭示你的人性，你觉得你得到的回应是什么？可能是彩带游行吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I am not going to be a spectator this evening, I am actually going to be part of the parade itself and I have the privilege of riding the Hong Kong Tourism Board Float and here she is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今晚我不只是观众，事实上我本人也是游行的一份子，而且我还荣获特许能搭乘上香港旅游局的彩车，就是这辆。

yingyinNormal.en: So, what time does the costume parade start? The parade?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那个服装展示什么时候开始？展示？

yingyinNormal.en: If you want to throw the newbie a parade, that's fine. Go ahead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你们想捧这个新人，无所谓，继续。
